{"lastModified":1771257377138,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::e6f0cd40-412d-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nOceanis 40.1 “Escape” (2024): Unleash Your Sailing Dreams\n\nIntroducing the Sailing Yacht Oceanis 40.1 “Escape” – a cutting-edge, brand new 2024 build that sets the standard for luxury and performance on the open seas. This meticulously designed yacht boasts a unique layout, making it the only vessel in its class to feature four spacious double cabins, ensuring unparalleled comfort for you and your guests.\n\nEquipped with the latest innovations, “Escape” redefines sailing excellence. The inclusion of air conditioning powered by shore connection ensures a cool and comfortable interior even in warmer climates. Embracing sustainability, the yacht is fitted with solar panels, harnessing the power of the sun to reduce environmental impact while maintaining efficiency.\n\nNavigating through the waters is a breeze with the Bowthruster, providing enhanced maneuverability and control. Whether you’re an experienced sailor or a novice, “Escape” makes sailing a joyous experience. The Semi Batten Mainsail further enhances performance, capturing the wind efficiently and allowing for a smooth and exhilarating sailing adventure.\n\n“Escape” is not just a yacht; it’s a statement of sophistication and functionality. Perfect for those seeking a balance of luxury and practicality, this vessel guarantees an unforgettable seafaring experience. Elevate your sailing journey with the Oceanis 40.1 “Escape” – where style, comfort, and performance converge.\n\nBook your voyage now and embark on a nautical adventure aboard the Oceanis 40.1 “Escape.” Discover the freedom of the open seas in a yacht that’s as unique as your sailing aspirations.\n","blueprint":{"name":"ESCAPE","images":["/media/media::image::c::8346777690::vessel::e6f0cd40-412d-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::17553780-5111-11f0-848d-add11adf76a4/{imageVariant}","/media